game.name: Office Strike
game.description:
The real fighting champion is waiting for you here! Would you like to practice your shooting abilities in a wonderful, engaging environment? If yes, Office Strike is the best platform for you to play online. This brand new action game is all about two girl teams who have no other choice except fighting to win supremacy in their office. Choose your girl and gear up to guide her to fight like never before in this highly challenging battle!

There will be a breakable interior in 4 different offices where this biggest fight of the planet will take place. You as a player will be allowed to choose your weapon out of several useful option. Feel free to use the sharp splinters of the destroyed items as a weapon in this HTML5 shooting game! Go through the office functions to browse through the effective secret buttons! Select any of the girls team between the Office Team and the Dominators!

Create your player name and room and then get ready to dive into the completely unique action world! Choose any option between the TeamDeathmatch and Deathmatch and allow yourself to witness the best fight you have ever experienced! Your room is full of professional players who cannot warn you before sending you to the God. Finalize your room and clear it from all the enemies to become the winner each time! Aim, fire and use any other weapon to destroy your opponents! Do not forget to reload your weapon to achieve your goal in this one of the best 3D shooter games for boys.
